text:
quizás te lo perdiste por la #navidad. pero el #24 de diciembre el actor #kevinspacey  publicó un vídeo interpretando a #frankunderwood, probablemente el personaje con el que será recordado. 
el discurso tiene al menos 2 sentidos. el primero dirigido sin duda alguna a #netflix y a los responsables de #houseofcards.

el segundo y más importante es a los medios de comunicación que más que informar sentenciaron al actor sin pruebas concretas tras la ola del movimiento #metoo. el mismo que ha manchado a personalidades como #neildegrassetyson y #morganfreeman sin pruebas tangibles por las solidaridades automáticas que genera el tema.  este también está dirigido a la audiencia a la que le cuestiona si creyeron todo lo que se dijo o por el contrario consideraron que  fue señalado ligeramente.

lo cierto es que su discurso está magistralmente armado. a diferencia de la 6ta temporada que no solo careció de discursos que te erizaran la piel, sino de coherencia, lo que es más grave.

en lo sucesivo la única demanda que se admitió en la corte contra #spacey pasará a juicio el 7 de enero.

nosotros estaremos atentos a este caso. ¿tú qué opinas de este tema?

#noticias #cine #peliculas #series #movimientometoo #venezuela

text:
хей-хо! кому идеи для новогодних подарков?!🎁
⠀ ⠀ 🎄подарок своими руками: всегда приятно, от души и индивидуально.❄️ можно сделать открытку (интернет пестрит крутыми праздничными идеями), испечь печенье и красиво упаковать, сплести венок из веток, прутиков или сделать из любых шариков, пробок, пуговиц, нанизав на основу. полет фантазии безграничен!
⠀ 🎄сертификат: всегда в точку, будь то карта в книжный или косметический магазин, посещение спа, квеструма, абонемент в любимый спортзал, ужин в ресторане.🛍 с этим угадать проще всего, а вариантов множество!
⠀ 🎄вещи с новогодней тематикой: фартук, милый плед, причудливый поднос или украшения на елку.🎅🏻 новый год праздник семейный и уютный, любой тематический подарок всегда будет приятен и усилит атмосферу праздника!
⠀ 🎄мягкая игрушка: новый год, как правило, возвращает нас в детство, а что лучше ассоциируется с ним как не милые «плюшки»?!
⠀ 🎄сладкий подарок: здесь история как с мягкой игрушкой, кому бы ты ни подарил, все будут радоваться как дети. 🍬 неважно сколько вам лет, заветный сундучок с «алёнкой», «невкусными» конфетами «на потом» и карамельками знаком каждому!
⠀ 🎄настольная игра: для семейного праздника – семейное занятие! согласитесь, партия в dixit, манчкина или монополию увлечет всех!👨‍👩‍👧‍👦
⠀
#подарокподелку #подароккрождеству #рождество #новыйгод #подарокмалышу #подарокотдедамороза #подарокновыйгод #подарокнановыйгод #pickygirl #пикигёл #pickygirlsofttoys  #metoo #metootoy #metoovrn #metoovoronezh #игрушкиворонеж #сплюшка #мягкаяигрушка #соннаяигрушка #мягкаяигрушкаворонеж #миту #подарок #митуворонеж #пики_инфо #идеяподарка #идеиподарков

text:
#sharethis would you like an endeared group  of yours to engage in conversation with me about girls and women??? let's talk. 
i did not know when writing #wecomeasgirlsweleaveaswomen this story would be read & used as a tool to strengthen a heightened discussion about #girls & #womanhood. i have conversed with groups of women, here i discuss with a co-ed group of high school seniors, soon, i will be having an intimate discussion with high school males only. and these men-to-be are currently reading the book before i arrive so we can really get down to business! girls are not the only ones who need to understand their complex routes to maturity-#boys and #men benefit from being made aware, too. and now. less #metoo experiences for our future when boys are taught early how to fully respect women and girls. #seriousbusiness #startthediscussionnow #read #everyone @amazon

text:
amazing news! as we all know, there have been many consequences of the #metoo movement worldwide. a recent study says that it may have actually contributed to reducing the stigma of sexual assault and similar types of abuse and harassment (based on a huge increase in related online searches), leading to more people seeking help and speaking out. this is a huge step forward for survivors. we have to keep speaking out and getting help. it's important to remember #youarenotalone 'the number of google searches related to sexual harassment or assault almost doubled as a result of the metoo movement, a study says.

the researchers said the results “suggest that metoo may have reduced the stigma of sexual harassment and/or assault as more seek help”.' read more at https://bit.ly/2epyxnf

text: mancano pochi giorni alla fine del #2018 ed eccomi a ripercorrere un intenso anno lavorativo. questo è il mio #bestnine in cui ho scelto alcuni degli articoli ho dedicato alle rivendicazioni e alle battaglie delle donne. i temi di genere sono quelli che sento più vicini perché mi permettono di esaudire la mia vocazione giornalistica che non può essere disgiunta dall’attivismo sociale. penso che i diritti delle donne debbano riguardare tutti. scrivere, parlarne, analizzare è decisivo. smantella i costrutti sociali, li può demolire. scrivere può costituire davvero una grande forza di cambiamento. dà parola al silenzio, al non detto. dà voce all’ingiustizia. negli stati uniti ha cambiato degli assetti tossici che sono rimasti a lungo immutabili. da noi il #metoo non ha avuto uguale forza pervasiva. per il #2019 serve ancora più coraggio, voglia di continuare a combattere, per portare avanti una rivoluzione che non può più essere rimandata #powertowomen #girlpower #revolution #activism #alleyoop #graziaitalia #mywork #feminism #women #rebel #picoftheday #photooftheday #journalism #writing #instadaily #instagood #news #actuality #best2018 #press #magazine #articles

recomendamos el libro " dramaturgas del siglo xxi", antología recopilada por la editorial catedra, letras hispánicas.
las autoras incluidas en este libro, presentan preocupaciones y procedimientos dramatúrgicos semejantes y abordan cuestiones fundamentales del panorama político, cultural y artístico de la actualidad. sus obras quieren convertirse en discursos cívicos y en amplificadores culturales. esta edición recoge obras de lola blasco, antonia bueno, diana de paco serrano, juana escabias, beth escudé i gallès, aizpea goenaga, diana i. luque, gracia morales, itziar pascual, carmen resino y vanesa sotelo. el volumen constituye una muestra muy significativa de las dramaturgias femeninas y del mejor teatro español de nuestros días.

text:
с клиентом всегда надо обращаться бережно, как с ребёнком 🤱🏼
он-самое дорогое, что у вас есть💎так же как детей 👼🏻знакомят с этим миром, также и вы знакомите клиента с вашим продуктом (это было в уроке 3). потом мы рассказываем и показываем, как с нашим миром продуктов можно взаимодействовать. вручаем ему ознакомительную литературу (учебники 📚) и проводим за руку до момента взросления и полного знакомства с продуктом (продажей)
поэтому помогите вашему клиенту сориентироваться в товаре, ваших постах, смыслах и пользе. отдельно обозначайте информативные посты от продажных, и от постов позиционирования! сделайте по ним навигацию! подпишите их наконец! если клиент увидел у вас интересный пост и вдруг каким-то магическим образом его другу понадобилась похожая информация! это сколько же контентом надо перелопатить, чтобы отыскать нужное❓
опять же, темы постов раскрывают суть аккаунта (бизнеса) и клиенту становится понятнее, куда он попал❗️

text: försvunnen syster senast sedd i ”samtyckesbutiken”. samtyckesbutiken. därinne står ett antal människor som säljer sina kroppar, du behöver bara läsa prislappen. därinne står jag, som behöver pengar till hyra, räkningar och busskort. psykiskt sjuk och för utmattad för att jobba, med en förälder som inte har råd att hjälpa till och 15+ års erfarenhet av att behaga män. där står jag i tjusiga underkläder, bredvid en annan som köpt ännu läckrare underkläder på martinshop och som fixat brösten. en tjej som inte har några föräldrar men som vill ha råd att köpa upplevelser och presenter till sina barn, som vill vara den förälder hon önskade ha. bredvid henne står någon vars namn jag behövde fråga hur man uttalar, och jag minns inte svaret. men jag minns att jag uppfattade att personen kollade runt åt alla håll och log nervöst hela tiden. jag uppfattade den som väldigt rädd. det står också en till person därinne som blundar hårt och pratar med sig själv. jag förstår inte vad den säger men jag noterar fuskdiamanten mellan benen som dinglar i dom svarta stringen. sen finns nadja. i adidas och kletigt smink, som kollar mig rakt i ögonen och ser helt förtvivlad ut. mannen drar en hand längsmed hennes ben och upp mot underlivet. jag ser henne i ögonen och viker inte blicken. ”500 swedish kronors” säger hon när hennes ögon skiftar från mig till honom. jag sväljer hårt. han pussar hennes axel och jag hör ljudet men jag ser inte längre. jag stirrar rakt ner i marken. kylan blåser länge över min kropp. jag blundar hårt och håller andan. dörren öppnas och stängs. jag har inte sett nadja sen den kvällen. det var 3 år sen. pga henne och alla andra som oss finns jag här. och håller aldrig käften. #intedinhora #metoo #prostitution

text:
i want to share my story. from the multiple incidents of sexual violence, abuse, catcalling, eve-teasing - this is the most recent.

i am a solo traveller and i blog about my travels. i want to present a true picture of my travels and not just insta-worthy glam shots that would make the world jealous of me. this might not be the most life-shattering stalking incident but every girl knows the fear and anxiety of something like this because in the moment, we don't know if we'll get out of it unscathed.

so, this happened a year ago on my solo trip to pondicherry. while walking to the promenade on my first day in pondicherry, i noticed two men following me. i halted at a distance to substantiate my doubts. i wanted to be wrong. to my dismay, i wasn’t and they walked past me only to stand at a distance and wait for me to take the lead once again. i did and walked towards a crossing and stopped again to see where they’re going. they had probably seen my phone from behind and the google maps i was using, knew where i was headed, and so they took the calculated right. now, i was in a fix because that’s was i was headed. nevertheless, i took the left.

and thank god for museums! i quickly went in to get rid of my stalkers and spent about 40 minutes there – coming out relatively relieved and a little more informed.
.
.
under section 354d indian penal code 1860 (ipc), any man who follows a woman and contacts, or attempts to contact such woman to foster personal interaction repeatedly despite a clear indication of disinterest by such woman commits the offence of stalking.

stalking is punishable on first conviction with imprisonment of either description for a term which may extend to three years, and also with a fine.  on a second or subsequent conviction, stalking is punishable with imprisonment of either description for a term which may extend to five years and is also liable to a fine.
.
.
#metoo #standagainstharassment #reclaimthestreets #fightsexualharassment #endviolenceagainstwomen #standup4humanrights #timesup #humanrights #unwomen #unwomenindia

text: last time i posted about r. kelly, his defenders had a field day in my comments-but when have y’all ever known a little push back to stop me?! take a look at this trailer for lifetime’s 3 night docu-series airing jan 3rd. one of the main take aways here for me is “nobody cares because we were black girls.” my goodness. decades later and still no accountability. this is a prime example of when celebrity worship goes wrong. it also shows that when the victims are black women and girls in cases like these, the scales of justice don’t often tip in our favor. @lifetimetv

text: i höstas släpptes boken "kvinnorna i hälsingland", skriven av två fantastiska journalister: lilian sjölund och malena hilding. reportageboken består av intervjuer och porträtt på 24 "starka hälsingekvinnor" där jag hedrande nog fick vara en. mitt reportage handlar om många olika saker – #metoo, relationen till hälsingland, varför jag valt civilsamhället i stället för partipolitiken och mycket annat, men framförallt om december 2013 då jag fick nog av den växande rasismen och bjöd in till ljusmanifestation i hudiksvall som samlade ett par tusen hudiksvallsbor. idag går den sjätte ljusmanifestationen mot rasism av stapeln i hudik och jag önskar att alla ni som befinner er i närheten åker dit och deltar. för samhällets skull men också för er egen skull. det är få saker som ger så mycket hopp och styrka som att samlas fysiskt med andra personer för ett gemensamt mål. 16:30 från glysis! och när tågat tillsammans genom hudiksvall med facklor tycker jag att ni ska köpa boken – full av inspiration och kvinnokraft! #hudikmotrasism

text:
tohle bude takový mix všeho, ale především je to názor na bena afflecka. 🤔nerozporuji jeho nadání a nesmírně úspěšnou hereckou kariéru. jeho výkony ve filmech jako dogma, argo zmizelá, good will hunting, jsou prvotřídní a bezesporu v nich má velmi osobitý styl. 😊takže ho nemůžu úplně sejmout v otázce herectví a výběru rolí. tedy až na batmana (2020), tam tajně doufám, že dojde ještě ke změně v obsazení. 😏přesto se nemohu zbavit pocitu, že ve filmech i mimo ně, působí nesmírně arogantně. věřte mi, sleduji tunu rozhovorů z filmového světa, talk show, rozborů apod. takže mám představu o tom, jaký public image si ben vytváří. po vypuknutí skandálu s castingovým hollywood gaučem, si okamžitě umyl ruce od henryho weinsteina, se slovy, že neměl ponětí co dělal. čemuž mnoho ostatních hereckých insiderů nevěřilo, protože se vědělo, že se znali velmi dobře a dokonce se i objevily e-maily, ve kterých si vyměňovali své “zkušenosti.” teď je samozřejmě v damage control módu a propaguje feminismus, politickou korektnost, islám atd. s čímž bych neměl nejmenší problém za předpokladu, že by tyto názory zastával před celou kauzou. 🤥
svou platformu slávy a vlivu využívá k propagaci svých relativně extremistických politických názorů. nechci říct, že člověk kvůli těžce získané slávě ztrácí právo na názor, ale měla by fungovat určitá umírněnost a opatrnost. nemluvě o tom, že v politickém rozhovoru s bill maherem, se ukázala i jeho neznalost základních témat a značná ignorance. 😤prohazovat slova jako rasistický, homofobní, antisemitistický je velmi nebezpečné a je to o to nebezpečnější u lidí, kteří mají silný vliv na ostatní, ale přitom nemají páru o čem mluví. hm, teď jsem tak nějak definoval většinu politiků right? 🤔no to je fuk, tohle je můj obrázek o benu affleckovi, několik dobrých filmů pod páskem, ale osobně bych ho poznat snad ani nechtěl.😒 #benaffleck #argo #dogma #cz #sk #czechboy #czechgirl #slovakgirl #slovakboy #filmy #zajimavosti #metoo #hollywood #opinion #followme

text:
i've watched the qspiracy since the beginning.

steve bannon left the wh august last year and q appeared the following october. do you believe in coincidences? church militant, anyone?

abusing and leaking presidential information to mislead the people and benefit a hijacked party is obviously just business as usual.

however - while doing this djt with the brave bunch known as gop has willingly opened a pussy wound that anyone around the world can easily contaminate. i like to call it meddlin' with presidental blessin'. i'm not the only one who knows this opportunity and messes with the boombastic patriots - may be russia or china or mbs or antifa or me me me, a tiny quarter pounder sitting on me me me bed. obviously someone has a lot to lose when none of the us intelligence agencies ends this loonatic travesty.

qshow seems like a vile roleplay but instead it has become the heart of the propaganda operation that joseph goebbels would have died for. it is clear that stuff like pizzagate™ was testing and groundwork for the 2016 election and since it proved to be very effective it is used still.

the accompanying memes go way beyond the propaganda of nsdap. social media companies are helpless with the content - no way they are going to risk their business by taking responsibility.

there is absolutely no way that gop isn't aware of what is going on - after all cambridge analytica worked for ted cruz and john bolton. the whole narrative is built on the same facebook user data that bannon and the mercers reportedly got from cambridge analytica.

trump is truly playing along with his tweets, gestures and words. the bigger issue still is that republicans willingly piggybacked this lunacy while campaigning for the midterms and still keep abusing the faith of their fellow men.

this is not just an insane national security risk - it's a leaking conspiracy and treason in plain sight.

text:
वो कहते हैं ना, जहाँ चाह है, वहां राह भी है। ठीक उसी तरह जब 2012 में हम निकले थे यह सोच कर की दुनिया में बदलाव लेकर आएंगे, और देखिये, आज बदलाव आ गया है। कुछ सालों पहले जब कहीं महिलाएं मासिक धर्म के बारे में कानों में फुस फुसा कर बातें किया करती थी, आज वही महिलाएं खुल कर सबके आगे, एक पूरी समाज सभा के सामने अपना अधिकार, अपने सेनेटरी नैपकिन उठाएं खड़ी हैं। यह दृश्य देख कर आँखें नम हो जाती हैं कि ज़्यादा ना सही, पर थोड़ा तो बदलाव आ रहा है। _______________________________

translation: just like they say, where there's a will, there's a way. so, just like that when we stepped out in 2012, we had a vision in our mind that we'll make a change in the world and today, we can absolutely say that the change is here.

few years ago, when women who used to feel uncomfortable while talking to other women about their menstruation. today, the same women are standing confidently in front of their community gathering, holding sanitary napkins.

eyes get wet when we see this sight. even though, the change has been low, but still we can see the difference.

#ngojeevanarthfoundation #jeevanarthfoundation #ngo #india #rajasthan #jaipur #womenempowerment #metoo #childeducation #girlchild #womensrights #equality #rights #education #society #dogood #philanthropist #socialservice #socialwelfare #donation

text:
que planea la elite mundial? seguramente abra problemas en roma.. aún no todo esta al descubierto, hay palabras de forma espetacular del vitruibio de davinci. el hombre es perfecto para yahweh.  segun la portada la elite tiene algo diferente como el hombre ideal. habla de guerra donde hay guerra hay pestilencia y hambruna.. el control de la humanidad atraves de la ilusión. yahweh se vale todo para cumplir sus profecias. como la gente ha rechazado a yahweh  y su bendita torah, envia un poder engañoso para que se pierda, eso dice  tanaj. en la portada vemos el apocalipsis en movimiento. en el 2019 davinci cumple 500 años de muerto. en la cara del hombre vemos unos lentes de realidad virtual eso es lo que la elite quiere tener contralada a la gente. por medio de la ilusión que tiene que con el ego la ilusoria percepción. señalaré algunos fragmentos de la simbología de la portada original, no todos. podría ser incorrecto, por supuesto, pero esto es lo que estoy viendo hacia la parte superior derecha, bajo "reconocimiento facial", verá una pintura de davinci titulada "cabeza de un anciano de perfil, copia de fax y". si investigas esto, implica la clonación humana.
frente a él se encuentra la imagen de la cara de trump con medidas dimensionales similares. esto significa que se mide. lo que se mide se rige. básicamente diciendo que lo poseen o que serán dueños de un clon que hacen de él.
new horizons to ultima thule: la nave espacial new horizons ha sido enviada al objeto kuiper belt 2014 mu69; un cometa llamado "ultima thule" que es "1.000 veces más masivo que los cometas típicos", por alguna razón. te dejaré averiguar por qué.
también tenga en cuenta la ubicación de los objetos 
las tuberías de putin: lo más probable es que se refieran al acuerdo energético entre rusia y china. también tenga en cuenta las mayores amenazas a los estados unidos. esto es confirmado por putin y el "panda enojado" (china) que mira hacia el oeste hacia américa. tenga en cuenta los cuatro jinetes, donde están de pie y donde se enfrentan. >>> parte 2>>>

text:
a few months later, in autumn 2013, wylie met steve bannon. at the time, he was editor-in-chief of breitbart, which he had brought to britain to support his friend nigel farage in his mission to take britain out of the european union.

what was he like? - smart, says wylie. - interesting. really interested in ideas. he’s the only straight man i’ve ever talked to about intersectional feminist theory. he saw its relevance straightaway to the oppressions that conservative, young white men feel.

wylie meeting bannon was the moment petrol was poured on a flickering flame. wylie lives for ideas. he speaks 19 to the dozen for hours at a time. he had a theory to prove. and at the time, this was a purely intellectual problem. politics was like fashion, he told bannon.

carole cadwalladr
the guardian

text:
este artigo bem poderia se chamar, à moda de stieg larsson, o autor de millenium, “os homens que temiam as mulheres”. porque é disso que se trata. mais de um ano depois do início do movimento metoo, começa a surgir uma reação contrária, que os analistas batizaram como efeito pence.
o nome alude ao vice-presidente dos estados unidos, mike pence. aqui ele é pouco conhecido, ofuscado que está por esse holofote de notícias alaranjado chamado donald trump. mas nos estados unidos, claro, pence é um personagem respeitado e respeitável, especialmente entre os religiosos. em março de 2017, numa reportagem sobre a mulher de pence, karen, dizia-se o seguinte a respeito dele: “nunca janta com uma mulher que não seja sua esposa”. seu exemplo, o de reduzir a convivência com as mulheres à sua relação sentimental, evitando o contato no ambiente profissional, parece se estender agora a outros âmbitos.
o primeiro a dar o alarme foi o canal de informação econômica bloomberg. seu artigo começava com uma espécie de impressionante tábua de mandamentos sobre como “evitar as mulheres a qualquer preço”: “não jante com colegas. não sente ao seu lado nos aviões. reserve quartos de hotel em andares diferentes. evite as reuniões individuais”. depois eram mencionadas mais práticas para evitar o contato feminino: manter as reuniões sempre com a porta aberta, nunca com mulheres menores de 35 anos, o mais longe possível no elevador… a reportagem se centrava no mundo de wall street, onde as mulheres não são particularmente numerosas, e corre-se o risco de que as poucas restantes desapareçam, virando um clube do bolinha. a paranoia de que possam ser denunciados por assédio sexual parece se espalhar por todo o distrito financeiro, conforme revelavam as entrevistas com até 30 altos executivos.
leia mais neste post.
fonte: el país

text:
안양예술고등학교 동아리 프락치🎩입니다
프락치라는 단어의 뜻은 원래 좋게 사용되지는 않지만 학생이라는 신분으로 비밀리에 활동하는 것에 중점을 둔 동아리명입니다
저희는 올해 미투운동에 관련된 뱃지와 엽서를 제작하여 판매하는 활동을 하고 있습니다
미투운동이란 미국에서 시작된 해시태그 운동입니다. 
2017년 10월 할리우드 유명 영화제작자인 하비 와인스틴의 성추문을 폭로하고 비난하기 위해, 소셜 미디어에 해시태그(#metoo)를 다는 행동에서 출발했습니다.
저희 동아리의 뱃지 모티브는 중국에서의 미투인데요
중국에서는 미투라는 말을 국가에서 금지시켰다고합니다😥
그런데 벼와 토끼를 합친 말이 미투 라는 말과 비슷해서 중국에서 미투운동을 지지할때 
토끼와 벼를 사용한다고합니다🤩🤩
간접적으로 표현한것이지요
그렇기에 저희도 이 뱃지를 통해 미투 운동을 하시는 분들의 주장을 간접적으로나마 지지하고자하여 만들게 된 것입니다

이 뱃지와 엽서를 판매하여 미투운동을 지지하는 단체에 기부하려고 합니다

뱃지 1개에 2000원
뱃지 2개에 3000원

안양예술고등학교 동아리 프락치🎩입니다
프락치라는 단어의 뜻은 원래 좋게 사용되지는 않지만 학생이라는 신분으로 비밀리에 활동하는 것에 중점을 둔 동아리명입니다
저희는 올해 미투운동에 관련된 뱃지와 엽서를 제작하여 판매하는 활동을 하고 있습니다
미투운동이란 미국에서 시작된 해시태그 운동입니다. 
2017년 10월 할리우드 유명 영화제작자인 하비 와인스틴의 성추문을 폭로하고 비난하기 위해, 소셜 미디어에 해시태그(#metoo)를 다는 행동에서 출발했습니다.
저희 동아리의 뱃지 모티브는 중국에서의 미투인데요
중국에서는 미투라는 말을 국가에서 금지시켰다고합니다😥
그런데 벼와 토끼를 합친 말이 미투 라는 말과 비슷해서 중국에서 미투운동을 지지할때 
토끼와 벼를 사용한다고합니다🤩🤩
간접적으로 표현한것이지요
그렇기에 저희도 이 뱃지를 통해 미투 운동을 하시는 분들의 주장을 간접적으로나마 지지하고자하여 만들게 된 것입니다

이 뱃지와 엽서를 판매하여 미투운동을 지지하는 단체에 기부하려고 합니다

뱃지 1개에 2000원
뱃지 2개에 3000원

엽서 3장에 1000원 에 판매하고 있습니다 ⭐️배송비 2500원은 별도입니다(안양예고 학생들은 배송비가 따로 없으니 저희 동아리 학생들에게 연락주시거나 저희가 지나갈때 말씀해주세요!) 구매의사가 있으신 분들은 아래 링크로 들어오셔서 성함, 주소,수량,상품명을 적어주시면 감사하겠습니다 😃

100개 한정수량!
1월 30일까지 수량 다 차면 마감하겠습니다!
(만약 그 전까지 마감된다면 따로 댓글 달겠습니다) 😂#미투#metoo#뱃지#엽서#고등학교#안양예술공학교#안양예고#고1#고2#고3#동아리#기부#일상#활동#뿌듯#도움#많은관심#부탁드립니다#홍보#화이팅#프락치

od a po z, tak by se dala nazvat tradice společných lovů na svátek sv. štěpána. z lesa až do hrnce. tady jí máte v obrazech. připomíná doby, kdy se pro jídlo nechodilo do supermarketů, ale do lesa. kdo neměl odvahu a schopnosti, ten měl v bříšku prázdno, ale zase nikdo nevymýšlel hovadiny. muž byl lovec. jedno zda mu skráně pokrývaly šediny nebo mu bylo třeba šest. prostě práce pro chlapy, ale i pro ženy, které sice o #metoo nesmýšlejí pozitivně, feministkám se smějí, ale místo toho umí vzít do ruky klidně i flintu. 😎😁

- "take a good look at the 33rd! edition of the #economist telling you in your face the state of the staged world in the upcoming episode of this ritualistic reality show that we have all unwillingly taken part in.
what does a stork usually carry in a bag? yeah, a baby...only this time the "product" has a barcode and a serial number on it as it is shipped from a supposed poor region (poor weirdo ghandi) of the world to the western land of the electric cars...someone should get on that serial number to decode it...and that vitruvian man with a night vision/virtual reality gear on...
•
all the satanic mirrored spells aside, "putin's pipelines" is written right above the depiction of the four horsemen of the apocalypse to come at the end of the world symbolizing conquest, war, famine, and plague/death...
•

text:
10 reasons why it pays to be a feminist

manny people think feminism is a dirty word reserved for angry women with armpit hair. whether you take this stance or believe that it should be shouted in the streets and celebrated as the equality amongst sexes it stands for, there are multiple reasons why it pays to be a feminist. male or female, feminism bridges the gap, and liberates all people from tainted beliefs and false narratives. men are expected to act a certain way, and women are expected to do the same. meanwhile, we are all stuck pointing fingers and accusing one another when all we need to do is open the floor to conversation on acceptance and understanding. shattering false narratives and building new ones for the benefit of all is what it's all about. we are all equal—regardless of our sex, gender, or race. failing to recognize this is what has gotten us in a lot of the trouble we experience today.

text:
#artist
🧁最近社群討論度很高的《水行俠》，大家看了嗎？
⠀
🌟飾演「梅拉公主」的安柏．赫德（amber heard），自 2004 年展開她的戲劇之路，雖然大多飾演配角，但私下的她勇敢又充滿自信，非常熱愛文學，關心難民、同志與婦女的權益議題，這樣的個人魅力讓人無法忽視，不少人都被她圈粉。
⠀
在 2016 年時，她成為家暴話題的公眾人物，在離婚之後，她將自己的傷痛，轉化為一股力量，開始為家暴的受害者發聲，並開啟了協助受暴女性的計畫「#girlgaze」，曾說：「過去這一年我看見了 #metoo 運動帶動了社會的對話，討論性暴力如何影響女性的生活。這個運動使得保護女性不再是口號，更有了制度化的可能。現在我只希望透過正面發聲，讓勇敢談論性暴力的女性能獲得更多支持，希望大家能夠團結起來，去改變社會準則、輿論觀點，甚至是法律。」
⠀
安柏．赫德（amber heard）對於自己的戀愛傾向，也毫不迴避，大方公開自己是雙性戀，表示：「與愛情相關的事我非常開放，不分性別，也不會因此覺得被貼標籤。」
⠀

#artist
🧁最近社群討論度很高的《水行俠》，大家看了嗎？
⠀
🌟飾演「梅拉公主」的安柏．赫德（amber heard），自 2004 年展開她的戲劇之路，雖然大多飾演配角，但私下的她勇敢又充滿自信，非常熱愛文學，關心難民、同志與婦女的權益議題，這樣的個人魅力讓人無法忽視，不少人都被她圈粉。
⠀
在 2016 年時，她成為家暴話題的公眾人物，在離婚之後，她將自己的傷痛，轉化為一股力量，開始為家暴的受害者發聲，並開啟了協助受暴女性的計畫「#girlgaze」，曾說：「過去這一年我看見了 #metoo 運動帶動了社會的對話，討論性暴力如何影響女性的生活。這個運動使得保護女性不再是口號，更有了制度化的可能。現在我只希望透過正面發聲，讓勇敢談論性暴力的女性能獲得更多支持，希望大家能夠團結起來，去改變社會準則、輿論觀點，甚至是法律。」
⠀
安柏．赫德（amber heard）對於自己的戀愛傾向，也毫不迴避，大方公開自己是雙性戀，表示：「與愛情相關的事我非常開放，不分性別，也不會因此覺得被貼標籤。」
⠀
如此灑脫活出自我的安柏．赫德（amber heard），很難不被人喜愛吧🥰！
⠀

text:
2018 flashback :
kontroversi terbesar bollywood di tahun 2018 😯

bollywood terganggu oleh beberapa kontroversi tahun ini, yang memiliki efek buruk selama berbulan-bulan. sementara film-film seperti padmaavat dan manmarziyaan harus menderita dahulu sebelum mendapat rilisnya, bintang-bintang seperti sidharth malhotra dan kangana ranaut harus mengeluarkan klarifikasi atas penyataannya. 
1. gerakan me too
mantan aktris tanushree dutta dan aktor nana patekar memulai kasus berkepanjangan ini. tanushree menuduh nana telah melakukan pelanggaran seksual selama syuting film horn ok pleassss (2008). atas kejadian ini, membuka suara dna menyeret beberapa yokoh bollywood atas kasus yang sama. tuduhan terhadap pembuat film vikas bahl yang menyebabkan spanduk produksi phantom films dibubarkan. aktor alok nath juga dituduh melakukan pemerkosaan oleh seorang penulis-produser tv. sutradara sajid khan harus keluar dari pengarahan film housefull 4, dan beberapa nama tokoh besar lainnya di bollywood.

2. padmaavat
perilisan film sanjay lela bhansali, padmaavat telah diliputi oleh protes besar. poster dari perangkat padmaavat telah dirusak pada bulan desember 2017 dan mengakibatkan penundaan rilis hingga januari 2018. masalah yang dimulai pada akhir 2017 merebak hingga 2018. beberapa kelompok rajput termasuk karni sena memprotes, merusak properti film, dan bahkan mengeluarkan ancaman kepada sanjay leela bhansali dan aktris utama deepika padukone. mereka mengklaim bahwa padmaavat menggambarkan ratu rajput padmavati dalam cahaya yang buruk. sementara beberapa negara melarang film tersebut, mahkamah agung menolak sebuah petisi untuk perilisannya.

rilis yang dijadwalkan pada 1 desember 2017 dengan judul 'padmavati' ditunda di india. akhirnya tiba pada tanggal 25 januari 2018, dengan judul yang berubah menjadi 'padmaavat', dengan beberapa potongan adegan. film ini akhirnya memecahkan beberapa rekor box office setelah dirilis.

3. sidharth malhotra - bhojpuri
kontroversi sidharth malhotra dan neetu chandra telah menuai perhatian publik. neetu chandra telah menampar keras sidharth malhotra karena...(selengkapnya baca difacebook) 😉

#indianexpress
#metoo
#padman
@padmaavat
#bhojpuri

text:
i am a feminist. i say this not because i think women are better than men or because i hate men, i don’t. i simply believe in gender equality.
the cambridge english dictionary gives the definition of feminism as "the belief that women should be allowed the same rights, power, and opportunities as men and be treated in the same way." more simply put; the idea that men and women should be treated equally. if you believe in gender equality, you therefore are by definition, a feminist. considering i can’t think of a valid reason as to why someone would not believe in gender equality, i undoubtedly believe that by these grounds, everyone should be a feminist. whether you actively involve yourself in the modern feminist movement is a choice, but equal rights shouldn’t be, and never should have been a debate. obviously there are ingrained, biological differences between men and women and we are clearly not the same, however this does not mean that either gender should be treated with any less respect or fewer rights. i’ll admit, the feminist movement has its flaws, but so does any movement, and there are varying degrees of extremity to the views held by those involved in and leading it. but this means we all have a choice; in what we believe and how far we believe it, and this choice is what makes feminism such a positive association

text:
feeling into so much gratitude for the opportunities, blessings and experiences 2018 has aligned me with. ⁣
⁣
i can honestly say that evolving empower the powerful has been the absolute highlight of my year if not life. ⁣
⁣
for the last 16 years i have only dreamed of creating something to pour my hearts passion into, which is to support survivors of sexual trauma absolutely and divinely thrive in life. ⁣
⁣
together we can break the silent global epidemic of what is, sexual violence. ⁣
⁣
together we can break the stigma around mental illness. ⁣
⁣
together we can live our wildest dreams. 
i hear you. ⁣
i believe you. ⁣
i see you. ⁣
i feel you. ⁣
⁣
mega love beams, kaity. (p.s. how epic is my office for the next 60 days here in bali)

text:
to all the enslaved african womxn who fought for womxn's liberation 
during the 500 year period of enslavement
to all the indigenous womxn who fought/fight against colonisation & imperialism
to all the domestic laborers who fought/fight corporate-agenda-serving labor laws
to all the the lesbian, queer, trans womxn who died fighting for all of our freedom to love and embody ourselves & who we choose to be
to all the mothers, aunties, sisters, cousins, daughters, who fight against childhood sexual assault in our homes, workplaces, in our streets
to the founders of black lives matter and the womxn who shoulder the movement 
to the civil rights movement womxn
to the black arts movement womxn
to the mau mau and the ahosi 
to nanny and amanirenas
to the guerilla womxn
to the courageous womxn unnamed
to the warrior womxn untamed
to the outcast and rejects 
the ones who will not stay quiet 
the ones who are hated & feared by the patriarchs & misogynists 
to the ones abandoned by our families in favor of abusers
to the survivors, the ones who are not liked nor loved
because we say no, because we resist
because we have no master
because we refuse to fall-in-line
we are not accomplices nor are we complacent
to the dangerous ones 
to the butus, the ghetto ones, the untouchables, the ratchets, the unrespectables, the whores, the sluts
the hags, the witches, the shit-disturbers, the bitches 
to all of us with a purpose & a promise on this earth

today, after 27 years 
i confronted the pedophile
the child sexual abuser
the molester of little black girls 
and my little black girl inside felt the deep love she desperately needed
from me. i stood up for her, even while terrified
i spoke up for myself, even while feeling bullied
today i understood the meaning of self-love
closure is the beginning 
of a new chapter
ase ancestors
thank you for walking with me
there is no equality without womxn's equality 
a revolution is brewing
-d’bi young anitafrika

text:
i would like to blame the holidays for missing my post on monday but, if i’m honest i have been under a major car of writers block. 
have you ever met a someone and just felt like you had to know them in anyway they’d let you? you know the feeling when you just crave someone? not even in an erotic way, just their mere company in the simplest of formats. maybe, that is the most intimate form of craving there is. 
but, what do i know? i’m just a gal hiding behind a typewriter.

text:
helpless and abused.
_
would you treat a #dog this way?
_
dairy’s dark secret
the typical dairy cow on a farm produces nearly 22,000 pounds of milk a year – more than double­ what its forebears did 40 years ago. they never graze; their hooves have rotted from standing in their own filth. their babies are taken away immediately, so the mom can produce milk. 
_
cows, like pigs, are social creatures; their babies are even more so. they nuzzle strangers, groan with pleasure when you pet them, and attach without complaint to callous minders. their sweetness gets them nowhere at auctions or at farms, however; the men and women working here smack them with boards and kick them in the haunches to move them forward. as one undercover investigator stated; “so common,” “saw guys punch them, stick cattle prods in their eyes, bragging, ‘i totally got her in the eyeball!’ it’s what happens when you do this long enough. they’re not your fellow creatures, they’re just trouble.
_
then there's the baby...a calf that can’t get up. its velveteen eyes are wet but blank; he barely stirs when jostled by other calves. “he got sick and gave up,” and so it goes with farmers who gave up farming to become cruel jailers of their "stock.” it’s like they hate their own animals for having feelings.”
_
how can you possibly justify this for a glass of milk, a piece of cheese, a bowl of #icecream ?there are so many plant-based alternatives available. please choose wisely. will your choices be responsible for creating more victims?

tweet_full:
helpless and abused.
_
would you treat a #dog this way?
_
dairy’s dark secret
the typical dairy cow on a farm produces nearly 22,000 pounds of milk a year – more than double­ what its forebears did 40 years ago. they never graze; their hooves have rotted from standing in their own filth. their babies are taken away immediately, so the mom can produce milk. 
_
cows, like pigs, are social creatures; their babies are even more so. they nuzzle strangers, groan with pleasure when you pet them, and attach without complaint to callous minders. their sweetness gets them nowhere at auctions or at farms, however; the men and women working here smack them with boards and kick them in the haunches to move them forward. as one undercover investigator stated; “so common,” “saw guys punch them, stick cattle prods in their eyes, bragging, ‘i totally got her in the eyeball!’ it’s what happens when you do this long enough. they’re not your fellow creatures, they’re just trouble.
_
then there's the baby...a calf that can’t get up. its velveteen eyes are wet but blank; he barely stirs when jostled by other calves. “he got sick and gave up,” and so it goes with farmers who gave up farming to become cruel jailers of their "stock.” it’s like they hate their own animals for having feelings.”
_
how can you possibly justify this for a glass of milk, a piece of cheese, a bowl of #icecream ?there are so many plant-based alternatives available. please choose wisely. will your choices be responsible for creating more victims?
_

text:
blast from the past. i found this with a few others in some boxes i am clearing out for mum before she moves and i leave for home to malta... photocopies of photo of me as found within my modelling portfolio ... me at 16 when i was a hopeful model. i still hate the way my lips sit in photos... my husband and i always have a laugh at my mouth in photos. i guess my parents encouraged me love for singing, dancing, writing and modelling to some extent and here is proof.
.
i wish i could talk to the 16 year old me and tell her to stay strong and tough, to take no shit and that being loved and adored is not a basic human need, only a myth to make girls feel needy and act passive to keep men in power and hold up the illusion that women are not an equal part of this world.
.
.
.
.

text:
today marks my 18 year hijab-aversary. wow. when i think back to what my life looked like when i chose to be the first and only person in my immediate family to wear the hijab and how that decision has defined me, my identity and my life since, i am in awe. i would have it no other way.
🧕🏽
making the decision to wear the hijab was harder than most would think, and not for the reasons many assume. i had to fight against my own family initially to wear it. they were afraid in part of what others would think and how i might be treated. what they did not realize however is how it would empower me to find my voice. in standing up for my decision to choose to wear the hijab to my family, i found the resolve i needed to defend my choice to strangers.
🧕🏽
no woman should ever be told how to dress or how not to dress. my hijab is an integral part of the woman i am and i wear it with an honour and pride i cannot even begin to describe.
🧕🏽
📸: @visual.fascination taken at the @cpact.ca annual meeting
🧕🏽

text:
on jubilee street
there was a girl named bee
she had a history
but she had no past
when they shut her down
the russians moved in
i’m too scared, i’m too scared
to even walk on past
she used to say
all those good people
down on jubilee street
they ought to practice what they preach
those good people
on jubilee street
and here i come up the hill
i’m pushing my wheel of love
i got love in my tummy
and a tiny little pain
and a ten ton catastrophe
on a sixty pound chain
and i’m pushing
my wheel of love up jubilee street
oh look at me now

the problem was
she had a little black book
and my name was written on every page
well a girl’s got to make ends meet
even down on jubilee street
i was out of place and time
and over the hill
and out of my mind
on jubilee street
i ought to practice what i preach
these days i go down town
in my tie and tails
i got a foetus on a leash
i am alone now
i am beyond recriminations
the curtains are shut
the furniture has gone
i am transforming
i am vibrating
i am glowing
i am flying

look at me now

nick cave

on jubilee street

i am alone now

the cuains are shut
the furniture has gone
i am transforming
i am vibrating
i am glowing
i am flying

look at me now

nick cave

text:
촬영이 있었더랬죠"
얼마전.
트랜드라는것에 민감했던 지난시간들이 값지고 소중하고 나를 있게 하는 것이였는데 (열심히했어.칭찬해)
잠시 나를 뒤흔들어 깨우고 어두웠던 나의 생각에 등불을 밝혀주는 시간이였습니다.
지구라는 별에서 여자로 살아간다는건
옳고그름을 알기전, no✋라고 말하기 전
부끄러움과 수치심을 먼저 받아들여야했죠.
#metoo #withyou

사실 아직도 어렵습니다.

이건 여자남자라기보단 사실 권력관계가 더 맞구요.

남들눈에 좋아보이는 카페주인장도 그 노출로부터 자유롭지못합니다. 보통은 돈만 많고 개념을 동물에게 줘버린 건물주들에게 여자카페주인은 권력앞에 힘없이 무너지기 좋은 많은 조건을 가지고 있으니까요.(누군가에게 전해들었죠) 그리고 시골에서 카페를 하는건 더 더욱이 퉷퉷. 
부끄럼움없이 동물들도 비웃을 이성을 가지고 카페에 왔다가기도하니까요. 보통이 자신이 그런*인줄 모르는거죠.
허허.

사실 좋은 분들이 더 많아요. 좋아해주시고 감사한 마음 담아가시고 기분좋은 머무름하시는분들이 정말 훨씬 더 많아요. (감사해요😘 오늘도)
2018년을 마무리하며 먼지를 털어봤어요.

anyway. 한 해를 마무리 하며 귀한시간이였고 
방송은 27일 목요일 오늘밤 오후 9시30분 jtbc「이규연의스포트라이트」에서 함께하세요.

오늘도 고마워요.잘 지내요 우리"
안녕히.

부끄럼움없이 동물들도 비웃을 이성을 가지고 카페에 왔다가기도하니까요. 보통이 자신이 그런*인줄 모르는거죠.
허허.

사실 좋은 분들이 더 많아요. 좋아해주시고 감사한 마음 담아가시고 기분좋은 머무름하시는분들이 정말 훨씬 더 많아요. (감사해요😘 오늘도)
2018년을 마무리하며 먼지를 털어봤어요.

오늘도 고마워요.잘 지내요 우리"

steve bannon left the wh august last year and q appeared the following october. do you believe in coincidences? church militant, anyone?

abusing and leaking presidential information to mislead the people and benefit a hijacked party is obviously just business as usual.

however - while doing this djt with the brave bunch known as gop has willingly opened a pussy wound that anyone around the world can easily contaminate. i like to call it meddlin' with presidental blessin'. i'm not the only one who knows this opportunity and messes with the boombastic patriots - may be russia or china or mbs or antifa or me me me, a tiny quarter pounder sitting on me me me bed. obviously someone has a lot to lose when none of the us intelligence agencies ends this loonatic travesty.

trump is truly playing along with his tweets, gestures and words. the bigger issue still is that republicans willingly piggybacked this lunacy while campaigning for the midterms and still keep abusing the faith of their fellow men.

this is not just an insane national security risk - it's a leaking conspiracy and treason in plain sight.

text:
this picture was 3 yrs ago.

i was sitting on the kitchen floor playing music for my daughter so she could dance.

i was also in the middle of a ptsd episode.

it's not easy to have come this far.

to live almost ptsd free.

it's a combination of so much work.

work that only made things far worse before they ever got better.

it was a combination of
energetic
akashic
physical
yogic
chakra
plant
soul retrieval 
and so much prayer.

when you add ptsd to hyper sensitive and sensory processing disorder it can make normal live unbearable.

but it can also make life very legit.💖💖💖 we aren't all wired exactly the same.

we don't all need the same teachers.

we don't all need the same medicine.

long term suffering is unneccassary .

here for the renegades and the white wolves. i don't have all the fucking answers but i can definetly light the way.

text: forgot i had the original from this photo shoot in new york, 1997. it was used on the cover of one of my comp cards and i had an agent who wanted to book me as a bond girl, at the time, and supposedly was tight with the broccolis of eon productions, then something happened and the agency closed and i just went to europe instead. what is amazing now, as i was just sharing this with a new friend while getting the picture out to post, is my life experiences have had such amazing turns that i would really prefer to play a role like m than be a bond girl now anyway! more age and experience appropriate, if i ever were to reconsider a direction in acting...life is something isn’t it, hm. 😉❤️ #metoo #metoomovement #timesup #autism #autismspeaks #tulsa #oklahoma #fashionfotoge #fashionfotog #fashionfotogevita #evita #model #photographer #writer #travelwriter #manager #actor #talent #wildlifephotographer #wildlife #fashionphotographer #runwaycoach #actingcoach #videographer #artdirector #copywriter #graphicdesign #advertising #musicphotographer #petportraits

text: one of my first modeling photos, as i was c. 19 or 20 and got started later than most models...as my fam was totally against it, for the most irrational reasons at the time, since they knew nothing about the industry and had a thinking style that did not set me up for success. that said, i pushed beyond the mysoginy working against a chance at a better life and to earn a great deal, by working full time as an electrical engineering assistant, while caving in to go to college, yet paying my own way, working full time, going to college part time, and driving hours to start modeling on days i could get off, until i got to ny. fighting ignorance and ego issues taught me tenacity, but cost me critical years to earn as a model and the impoverished thinking style i was raised with set me up to be vulnerable to predators in the business. though it cost me, i never caved into the predators and eventually paid the price by getting stalked out of the business and harassed by a few dishonorable personalities...and still i grew, and learned, and empowered myself and continue to overcome and become all i can be as a woman of strength in her convictions...now for the sake of showing others who may benefit what i learned to ease their path toward success and autonomy. 👍 #metoo #metoomovement #timesup #autism #autismspeaks #tulsa #oklahoma #fashionfotoge #fashionfotog #fashionfotogevita #evita #model #photographer #writer #travelwriter #manager #actor #talent #wildlifephotographer #wildlife #fashionphotographer #runwaycoach #actingcoach #videographer #artdirector #copywriter #graphicdesign #advertising #musicphotographer #petportraits
name: Fashion Fotog

text: almost 50 and no plastic surgery...however!, i cheated with a lot of the right lighting choices, to make my skin look less tired and younger! photo from about a year ish ago and seeing the horizon of fifty coming...however, as one who used to be against plastic surgery and lost out on opportunities because i was grossed out by the idea i should get a nose job, like other models did, to book the major campaigns (retouching your own pics was a no-no and only done by the magazines until, it seems c. 2001 ish, when i was getting out the biz it seems)...however, as aging progresses and non-invasive more natural procedures have developed now, i totally understand the temptation to tighten it up! lol! in truth, mommyhood is the priority for me, so it’s a very back burner issue and cost-intensive anyway, but thought i’d chime in (when i had a moment) on the cultural normalcy bias shifting per plastic surgery versus the quiet way models did it when i modeled! interesting world we live in...😉! #metoo #metoomovement #timesup #autism #autismspeaks #tulsa #oklahoma #fashionfotoge #fashionfotog #fashionfotogevita #evita #model #photographer #writer #travelwriter #manager #actor #talent #wildlifephotographer #wildlife #fashionphotographer #runwaycoach #actingcoach #videographer #artdirector #copywriter #graphicdesign #advertising #musicphotographer #petportraits

text: “on a very personal note, my mother, who passed when i was ten, from cancer, and without knowing i would lose, then find this letter only after i started modeling years later, taught me beauty in its whole truth and exhibition...her legacy for me was to articulate and illustrate it as a gift to lift others, and not to define myself as a token of beauty. though i never operated as though there are not so many other people in the world whose beauty, intellect, talent and accomplishments had or could, surpass mine any day of the week and still do often esteem others higher than self, as is the definition of true grace in my opinion...how truly beautiful was my mother, to gift this eternal wisdom to me, whose very essence was as the lilt of an american beauty, my favorite rose, by the way...fragile, delicate to the touch, yet vibrant and even potent in its depth of colour...that, by virtue of such, eminates a radiance with an impact that is no less than everlasting. that...and nothing less, is the true definition of beauty...it is...love in motion...as it should be ‘in earth as it is in heaven.’” “walk in peace and love so we can show the way back home.” by evita e.  #metoo #metoomovement #timesup #autism #autismspeaks #tulsa #oklahoma #fashionfotoge #fashionfotog #fashionfotogevita #evita #model #photographer #writer #travelwriter #manager #actor #talent #wildlifephotographer #wildlife #fashionphotographer #runwaycoach #actingcoach #videographer #artdirector #copywriter #graphicdesign #advertising #musicphotographer #petportraits

text: this is one of my first fashion images of a girl in atlanta who looked a lot like sade, in person, though a bit less on camera. still, she had potential and had done some small acting parts, but was not someone who seemed motivated to do much more as we chatted in general. and, that is one of the reasons it took me years to consider managing, or even being a booker. because, when i would help other model friends arrange their “books” or teach them a better walk, i still could not help them find the tenacity in themselves the industry requires, and some even lacked the level of integrity one would hope for in a friend, or from a potential business perspective...such as one who, like my ex, would take my ideas and present them as her own. but, things happen the way they do and years later i feel much more seasoned or better equipped to guide talent, on many levels of the industry, with a strong desire to see good people flourish! - as well as, more polished in my own artistry that continues to develop too, behind the camera, etc. so, the take away is if i present a model, or talent, with the knowledge or opportunity to get to the next level and they do not take it, then it is their choice and managing is still something that interests me as an ornament on tree of my emerging renaissance...and i look forward to avenues to exercise my skills and interests; especially, when they culminate in win-wins! ❤️❤️ #metoo #metoomovement #timesup #autism #autismspeaks #tulsa #oklahoma #fashionfotoge #fashionfotog #fashionfotogevita #evita #model #photographer #writer #travelwriter #manager #actor #talent #wildlifephotographer #wildlife #fashionphotographer #runwaycoach #actingcoach #videographer #artdirector #copywriter #graphicdesign #advertising

🌱”never quiet your desire for infinity”

text:
"i am over rape. 
i am over women still being silent about rape, because they are made to believe it’s their fault. because they did something to make it happen like “wearing the wrong clothes.” i am over thinking about rape every day of my life since i was five years old. i’m over getting sick from rape. i’m over getting depressed from rape. i’m over getting enraged by rape. i’m over reading my insanely crowded inbox of rape horror stories every hour of every single day.

i am over being polite about rape. it’s been too long now, we have been too understanding. we need it to end now." ~eve ensler "over it"

#onebillionrising #untiltheviolencestops #vaginamonologues #riseresistunite #metoo

text:
i have to be a little selfish today and celebrate me for #wcw. •
•
i am far from perfect and i do not have (or ever had) a storybook perfect life. i have made countless mistakes and have more flaws than i can count. •
•
•
•
i celebrate me for being authentically and unapologetically me no matter what. god makes no mistakes and i’m so excited for where he is taking me next. 🙏🏾

text:
😞coping from childhood sexual abuse is daunting, and many survivors suffer from post-traumatic stress disorder.
.
😞overcoming shame, guilt, and self-blame, lead survivors to feel bad about themselves, and in most cases makes it hard for survivors trust anyone.
.
❤️although every case of abuse is different, and many survivors still live in silence, the effects of abuse are misunderstood, and leaves them feeling powerless years after the abuse is over.
.
.🤗although trying to cope day to day is daunting, and many survivors feel alone while healing, today is the day i want you to know you’re not alone, and i’m sending you lots of love, support, and understanding.
.
#healingfromabuse #ptsd #ptsdawareness #trauma #childhoodmemories #survivor #metoo #mentalhealth #speakout #endchildhoodsexualabuse #cope #trustissues #healthyboundaries #boundaries #anxiety

text:
a legacy
so far removed
one day will be improved
eternal rights
we left behind
we were the better kind
two the same, set free too

i always looked to you
i always looked to you
i always looked to you

we fought for good
stood side by side
our friendship never died
on stranger waves
the lows and highs
our vision touched the sky
immortalists with points to prove

i put my trust in you
i put my trust in you
i put my trust in you

a house somewhere
on foreign soil
where ageless lovers call
is this your goal
your final needs
where dogs and vultures eat
committed still i turn to go

i put my trust in you
i put my trust in you
i put my trust in you
i put my trust in you
in you. in you. in you
put my trust in you, in you

ian curtis

text:
hey trauma, the day we met....
.
i lost every ounce of dignity for myself. i often feel shackled to shame, guilt, self-hate, and fear. when we move from childhood into adulthood there are many roles/identities you dream of stepping into, but ‘survivor’ isn’t one of them! but here i am...an unexpected survivor of abuse.
.
i’m often told - almost demanded - to get over it or move on. sure, the bruises and bones have healed many times, but mentally i can’t get over the shame & pain of trauma. i feel nothing except worthless, sad, damaged from the inside out, unrecognizable.
.
for me trauma is this 20ft. wall that surrounds & blocks everything. is this surviving?
......anonymous✨
.
.
.

text:
i'm excited to announce the first official guest on january's episode of the survivor diaries podcast is my dear friend melanie. a survivor, thriver, writer, volunteer and advocate; mel is one of the most amazing souls i've ever known. 
in this upcoming episode, mel and i will chat about how our stories brought us together and how our connection helped us through some of our darkest moments.

i can't wait for you all to get to know mel and to hear her story, her strength blows me away and i am so thankful to have her in my life and as a part of my journey. 
in mel's words: "this journey isn’t easy or linear but it’s worth it."

•

text:
i've watched the qspiracy since the beginning.

steve bannon left the wh august last year and q appeared the following october. do you believe in coincidences? church militant, anyone?

abusing and leaking presidential information to mislead the people and benefit a hijacked party is obviously just business as usual.

however - while doing this djt with the brave bunch known as gop has willingly opened a pussy wound that anyone around the world can easily contaminate. i like to call it meddlin' with presidental blessin'. i'm not the only one who knows this opportunity and messes with the boombastic patriots - may be russia or china or mbs or antifa or me me me, a tiny quarter pounder sitting on me me me bed. obviously someone has a lot to lose when none of the us intelligence agencies ends this loonatic travesty.

qshow seems like a vile roleplay but instead it has become the heart of the propaganda operation that joseph goebbels would have died for. it is clear that stuff like pizzagate™ was testing and groundwork for the 2016 election and since it proved to be very effective it is used still.

the accompanying memes go way beyond the propaganda of nsdap. social media companies are helpless with the content - no way they are going to risk their business by taking responsibility.

there is absolutely no way that gop isn't aware of what is going on - after all cambridge analytica worked for ted cruz and john bolton. the whole narrative is built on the same facebook user data that bannon and the mercers reportedly got from cambridge analytica.

trump is truly playing along with his tweets, gestures and words. the bigger issue still is that republicans willingly piggybacked this lunacy while campaigning for the midterms and still keep abusing the faith of their fellow men.

this is not just an insane national security risk - it's a leaking conspiracy and treason in plain sight.

text:
💀 𝕹𝖎𝖌𝖍𝖙𝖒𝖆𝖗𝖊 𝕭𝖊𝖋𝖔𝖗𝖊 𝕮𝖍𝖗𝖎𝖘𝖙𝖒𝖆𝖘 💀
here's what i was wearing this sunday (dec 23rd 2018) when i was intimidated and verbally abused by a man twice my size for not returning his "merry christmas" or conceding to his demands to explain my alternative holiday & beliefs right there on the dance floor. 🔪
i'm a petite creature and i have been physically intimidated by men a lot in my life.  but i think it is really *interesting* that this always seems to happen to me when i am dressed #femme,  glamorous high femme, or sometimes without makeup and therefore i look even younger.  but it  hardly ever happens when i am dressed androgynous,  grungey, or downright boyish.
💀
aesthetics is what i do for a living, and costume is part of who i am,  so i will never stop dressing up... but its sad to me that entitled men see me as an easy target when i look like a bite sized femme. honestly it does make me think twice about wearing stuff like that out... i'm not even talking about revealing or "slutty" clothes,  im talking about projected gender & sexuality identity. 🔪
men don't pick fights with me when i "look like a lesbian" only when i "look like a little girl" - what does that tell you about how sick our culture is? 💀
i already blocked this man from my account but if he's not signed in he can still see this post... so this i say to him:
➡️do not cross my path again. ➡️do not underestimate me. ➡️do not forget that i am licensed to wield sharp objects. 🔪
my #battlecry of the week is #fightlikeagirl by @emilieautumnofficial
with additional shoutout to her song #thankgodimpretty :
🥄
"𝓣𝓱𝓪𝓷𝓴 𝓖𝓸𝓭 𝓘'𝓶 𝓹𝓻𝓮𝓽𝓽𝔂
𝓔𝓿𝓮𝓻𝔂 𝓼𝓴𝓲𝓵𝓵 𝓘 𝓮𝓿𝓮𝓻 𝓱𝓪𝓿𝓮
𝓦𝓲𝓵𝓵 𝓫𝓮 𝓲𝓷 𝓺𝓾𝓮𝓼𝓽𝓲𝓸𝓷
𝓔𝓿𝓮𝓻𝔂 𝓲𝓵𝓵 𝓽𝓱𝓪𝓽 𝓘 𝓶𝓾𝓼𝓽 𝓼𝓾𝓯𝓯𝓮𝓻
𝓒𝓵𝓮𝓪𝓻𝓵𝔂 𝓫𝓻𝓸𝓾𝓰𝓱𝓽 𝓸𝓷 𝓫𝔂 𝓶𝔂𝓼𝓮𝓵𝓯
𝓣𝓱𝓸𝓾𝓰𝓱 𝓽𝓱𝓮 𝓬𝓸𝓹𝓼 𝔀𝓸𝓾𝓵𝓭 𝓬𝓸𝓶𝓮
𝓕𝓸𝓻 𝓼𝓸𝓶𝓮𝓸𝓷𝓮 𝓮𝓵𝓼𝓮"
🖤
thanks for listening. 🔪🖤🔪🖤🔪🖤🔪

text:
i like to envision the new year this way, being granted the gift of more time. more opportunities to experience new things, to meet new people, more time to reach your dreams. ..
this time last year i was in so much pain, the nerve pain was overbearing and trying to walk even with the crutches was horrid. i spent my new years eve in hospital trying to get the pain under control... i was alone, crying and wanting to end my life... looking back, i can be proud of how much i got through this year and  it has been a year of big tests and realizations also. ..
i haven't felt so excited about the new year in quite a while. the prospect of what the year will bring feels very positive! i know that shit happens also but i am going to make the best of what the year brings to me 👌🏻😊💜💜💜🙌🏻 #bringon2019 #mentalhealthwarrior #traumasurvivor #healing #recovery #believeinyourself #love #life #youmatter #youcanhealyourlife #strength #support #healingthoughts #surviveandthrive #inspiration #time #gift #positivevibes #mentalhealthreminders #selflovethoughts #wellbeing #mentalwellness #yougotthis #positivereminders #quotetoliveby #metoo #sexualabuse #mentalhealthjourney

text: to those on a similar road..it has been a long road. a slow road. but a road i am glad i stepped on. the road before me is not, by any means, an easy one. but one i face now determined. i am relearning to do and wear what -i- actually, genuinely enjoy. for a very very long time what i "enjoyed" was based on if it made someone else happy or not. but slowly i started to get back to what i genuinly found pleasure in, found comfort in, felt good in. and slowly all the cracked and broken pieces are being forged whole again. in my minds eye it has the appearance of mercury glass. imperfect, but shiny and unique in its beauty. to those finding their feet on the path. keep going!! keep fighting!! you will make it and be far better for it. reclaim your special energy and don't look back!!!💖💗💖#selflove #selfcare #selfdiscovery #wellbeing #wellness #jusssayin #settingboundariesandfsu #thetruthturnsmeon #boundaries #nocontact #redflags #narcissist #narcissisticabuse #narcissism #metoo #abuse #crazymaking #traumabonding #emotionalabuse #toxicrelationships #survivor #gaslighting #toxicpeople  #mentalhealthawareness #domesticviolence #believewomen #ifmywoundswerevisible #dontlookback #narcissisticabusesurvivor

text:
i've watched the qspiracy since the beginning.

steve bannon left the wh august last year and q appeared the following october. do you believe in coincidences? church militant, anyone?

abusing and leaking presidential information to mislead the people and benefit a hijacked party is obviously just business as usual.

however - while doing this djt with the brave bunch known as gop has willingly opened a pussy wound that anyone around the world can easily contaminate. i like to call it meddlin' with presidental blessin'. i'm not the only one who knows this opportunity and messes with the boombastic patriots - may be russia or china or mbs or antifa or me me me, a tiny quarter pounder sitting on me me me bed. obviously someone has a lot to lose when none of the us intelligence agencies ends this loonatic travesty.

qshow seems like a vile roleplay but instead it has become the heart of the propaganda operation that joseph goebbels would have died for. it is clear that stuff like pizzagate™ was testing and groundwork for the 2016 election and since it proved to be very effective it is used still.

the accompanying memes go way beyond the propaganda of nsdap. social media companies are helpless with the content - no way they are going to risk their business by taking responsibility.

there is absolutely no way that gop isn't aware of what is going on - after all cambridge analytica worked for ted cruz and john bolton. the whole narrative is built on the same facebook user data that bannon and the mercers reportedly got from cambridge analytica.

trump is truly playing along with his tweets, gestures and words. the bigger issue still is that republicans willingly piggybacked this lunacy while campaigning for the midterms and still keep abusing the faith of their fellow men.

this is not just an insane national security risk - it's a leaking conspiracy and treason in plain sight.

text:
repito, la violencia es real.
con #metoo y #miprimeracoso, el mundo se ha enterado pero las mujeres lo hemos sabido siempre: no hay ni una sola que no haya vivido acoso, abuso, violación y las cifras oficiales se quedan cortas.
como parteras, vemos mucho que el abuso sexual que las mujeres vivieron resurge en el embarazo, en consultas ginecológicas, al hacer un tacto en el parto,... el cuerpo no olvida y el nervio pudendo menos.
por eso es tan importante que hagamos todo, todo, todo y más para asegurarnos que las mujeres sepan que ellas son las que tienen el poder en el proceso acompañado por nosotras. ya sea en el parto, en un papanicolau o en la puesta de un diu, como proveedoras debemos darles esa seguridad y confianza a las mujeres - con palabras y actos.
recuerdo el parto de una mujer con antecedentes de abuso que le seguía causando secuelas vaginales. ella temía que si le hacía un tacto, se tensaría mucho y no se lo podría hacer. yo le aseguraba que probablemente no sería necesario y si sí, podíamos trabajar muy lentamente, con ella en control siempre. cuando me pidió un tacto, me preguntó que si ella se podía meter mis dedos y así lo hicimos y fue muy sencillo.
después del parto vimos que hubo un desgarre que había que suturar. me preguntó que si ella se podía colocar la anestesia porque la ponía muy nerviosa que yo se la pusiera. y le di la jeringa, guié su mano y le señalé donde meter la aguja y la metió ella.
la atención centrada en la mujer es posible, importante y no debería ser algo que tengamos que negociar. como proveedoras la deberíamos ofrecer y practicar siempre. como mujeres no deberíamos aceptar menos.
como proveedoras, desgraciadamente tenemos que asumir de todas las mujeres que han vivido algún tipo de violencia sexual, aunque no lo digan. lo “peor” que puede pasar es que no lo vivieron y las tratamos bien. lo mejor: apoyar a que puedan resignificar sensaciones y emociones y saberse dueñas de ellas mismas y sus procesos.
#violenciasexual #violenciaobstetrica #reviviendotraumas #elpartopuedesanar #atencioncentradaenlamujer #feministmidwife #parterafeminista #womancenteredcare #laviolenciaobstetricatambienesviolenciasexual #estamoshartas

text:
ground palm strike ✋🏻& ground hammer fist 🤜🏻 .
.
.
.
i was doing this ground & pound drill in my workout today (i just love it) but you can definitely apply this for self-defense if needed. .
.
.
i am basically doing the palm strike and hammer fist to a target on the ground. .
.
.
for the ground palm strike i am using the heel of my palm as the surface area (curling my fingers back to get them out of the way).
.
.
.
for the ground hammer fist i am using the side of my fist as a surface area.
.
.
.
both strikes feel solid physically as i can strike harder using these surface areas.
.
.
.
if you practice this, make sure you have a good training pad that can take the impact. a really thick pillow, couch or mattress can also work if you need to get creative.
.
.
.
i also always recommend that anyone incorporating my drills do a few reps slowly and then gradually increase the speed or power to stay safe and prevent injury.
.
.
.

text:
wylie said that bannon's plans began to solidify in 2014, when cambridge analytica consulted various republican campaigns and pacs ahead of the midterm elections. the company began to test and apply its psychographics by using facebook data to model individuals' personality types in order to understand how to influence them.

documents show the john bolton super pac, which promoted candidates supported by recently appointed white house national security adviser john bolton, paid cambridge analytical $454,700 in 2014 for "behavioral microtargeting with psychographic messaging." those services included strategies that broke individual voters into "clusters" based on what messages would resonate with them.

wylie also said the company used focus groups and messaging trials in 2014 to test some of the concepts that became core themes of the trump campaign, such as "drain the swamp" and imagery of walls. "a lot of the narratives of the trump campaign were what we were testing in 2014," wylie said.

he added that bannon directly presided over much of the company's initial research. "everything that we were doing ultimately had to be passed up to bannon for approval," said wylie, who left the company in late 2014.

wylie said bannon would fly to london about once a month for company meetings, and during that time he came to understand bannon's ideology. "he really liked the idea of using a military-style approach to changing people's perceptions," wylie said.

curt devine, donie o'sullivan & drew griffin
cnn

text:
•d o  w h a t  y o u  e n j o y•

i’ve done p90x, insanity, piyo, yoga, zumba, classes at the ymca, and who knows what else.  none of it stuck.

i remember marking the workouts off the calendar included in the program, only to get to the end of the month and have several workouts i needed to make up 🙄i never enjoyed listening to shawn t anyway, so i stopped.

i found my love for backpacking/hiking in 2015 when a friend invited me to join her on the appalachian trail.  it was so rewarding hiking mountains everyday, then being so exhausted in the evening that i often ate my ramen noodle raw with a side of gummy worms. yum 😋 i wish i could do that everyday, but unfortunately there’s a major lack of mountains in northeast ohio.
☹️
it wasn’t until 2017 when my best friend invited me to a crossfit class with her.  i’ve been hooked since.  i love the challenge, community, and that everyday is different!  i’ve only done it for a total of 11 months, but it’s legit the only workout i consistently do and enjoy!
🏋🏼‍♀️
maybe crossfit isn’t your thing. that’s okay! just do something that actually brings you joy because if you love it you will keep doing it! & bless your heart if that’s running.  that’s a hard pass for me 🙅🏼‍♀️

tweet_full:
wylie said that bannon's plans began to solidify in 2014, when cambridge analytica consulted various republican campaigns and pacs ahead of the midterm elections. the company began to test and apply its psychographics by using facebook data to model individuals' personality types in order to understand how to influence them.

documents show the john bolton super pac, which promoted candidates supported by recently appointed white house national security adviser john bolton, paid cambridge analytical $454,700 in 2014 for "behavioral microtargeting with psychographic messaging." those services included strategies that broke individual voters into "clusters" based on what messages would resonate with them.

wylie also said the company used focus groups and messaging trials in 2014 to test some of the concepts that became core themes of the trump campaign, such as "drain the swamp" and imagery of walls. "a lot of the narratives of the trump campaign were what we were testing in 2014," wylie said.

he added that bannon directly presided over much of the company's initial research. "everything that we were doing ultimately had to be passed up to bannon for approval," said wylie, who left the company in late 2014.

wylie said bannon would fly to london about once a month for company meetings, and during that time he came to understand bannon's ideology. "he really liked the idea of using a military-style approach to changing people's perceptions," wylie said.

text:
block them on instagram. delete their number. whenever your mind plays tricks on you and wants you to remember all the good times together, remind yourself that they were a wolf in sheep’s clothing.

my new life is so much better than my old one. but there was a cost to pay: everything. new friends. a new job. rebuilding my finances. finding a new bar to hangout at. skipping shows.

but that wasn’t even the hard part. i had to remind myself that my old life was a lie—at least on my abuser’s part. all those good times, all the times i thought my abuser might actually love me, i had to remind myself that those weren’t true. my abuser had an agenda. and that’s where it cost me. i didn’t want to believe that.

it all depends on the couple and how comfortable they feel. basically, some individuals don't like the idea, while some see it as a natural monthly break in the action, and others are perfectly comfortable with it. however you feel, just remember to talk it over with your partner beforehand to make sure you are on the same page. 
remember, having sex during her period, she can still get pregnant, and both partners can still contract stds. in fact, having sex during her period can make it easier to spread stds. so always use a condom every time you have sex.

it's rare, but possible... pornography can become a problem when it gets in the way of daily activities - like going to school or work or meeting with friends for social time. addiction to porn is considered to be a type of sexual addiction and can manifest itself differently than other types of sexual addictions. addiction to porn can also lead to serious distress and consequences in many facets of life.
the first step in getting help is admitting you have a problem, followed by finding a professional who is experienced in treating porn addiction and is aware of the most effective treatment methods, such as cognitive behavioral therapy (cbt). don't leave out important details because they are embarrassing and uncomfortable, because they can help guide your treatment plan. keep in mind that the therapist is there to help, not to judge.

text:
just ready to get out of the midwest. 
i am a city girl at heart who happens to love hiking and waterfalls, my heart does not belong in tulsa, oklahoma. 
i'm an introverted extrovert who needs time to myself, but gets lonely after so long and needs to talk to human beings. 
i am agnostic at best and i have no place in "the buckle of the bible belt."
i love dressing up, #yoga, #animals, #lgbtq+, #feminism, #equality, #democracy, #metoo, books, and #fundamentalrights.
i am a #vegetarian atm but am working to become #vegan.  i support #crueltyfree and vegan products.
i love the arts. #music, #theatre, #painting, #expression.
i am a published #authorillustrator of a children's book #thezoocrew
right now i am 100% dependant on ss disabilty income and my life savings, my paychecks never make it through the month.
i endure anorexia, depression, anxiety, ptsd, borderline personality disorder, and treatments of #electroconvulsivetherapy.
i believe in a family of choice.  i believe that no one should tell you how to believe.  i believe in rainbows and golden tickets that open up the doors to oppertunity. 
#amda is my golden ticket and my audition is april 7th :)

text:
i thought if i kept quiet it would get better, i thought i was reading into it, i was told nothing would change. 
on multiple occasions my boss said things that were inappropriate and made me feel uncomfortable. from commenting on my appearance, telling me he was addicted to sex, and the boss and other male employee looking at websites during a meeting and commenting on the females to me. (things like, “i’d buy this lingerie if she came with it”, “you should get this for your fiancé”) not to mention when i was called a “bitch” with no repercussions. when i decided to speak up, i was told it would backfire on me. i was told it would be considered drama and that it would cost me my job. 
after witnessing how chase operates, i have officially left banking.
i honestly hope something more than a slap on the wrist comes from this. 
for the manager to act that way towards another person, as a human being, it’s disgusting. whether female or male, it is not appropriate for someone to act this way towards another person; it is not appropriate for people who see things happening to feel as though they shouldn't stand up for what is right. 
how they handle this, will be my deciding factor on how chase is as a company.
#metoo #metoomovement #metoomvmt #metoostory #iwillnotbequiet #iwillnotbesilent #knowledgeispower #share #pleaseshare #makeadifference #makeachange #change #myvoice #myvoicecounts #beheard #letyourvoicebeheard #changesociety

text:
let's talk about multiple oppressions. inspired by @dev.manning. ••••
{quick trigger warning- mentions of slurs (never said explicitly), sexual assault, and gender dysphoria.}
i am a typically non passing, fem/andro expressing trans masc person who is also queer, neurodivergent, and a sexual assault survivor. there is not a minute that goes by which i do not have to be conscious of my identities. whether it is walking home and hearing slurs/cat calls (which i still get for some reason??), my mental health impacting my interactions with others and myself, or living with the worry of what the next person i meet might say. 
each form of oppression impacts the others. and many times i find them to be inseparable when i try to analyze them as individuals. 
the world around me sends clear messages that who i am is an unwelcome oddity. that i as a trans person am disgusting and that i can never live up to what it means to be cis in society. that i as a sexual assault survivor am lying, stretching the truth, or not getting over my traumas fast enough. that i as a neurodivergent person am "crazy", unlovable and irrational. 
i am working to unlearn these internalized messages because i know that i am not alone in experiencing them. i am working to understand the privileges i do have (i am able bodied, middle class, and white). it can be east to forget our privileges when we have multiple oppressed identities, but from my experience it is extremely important to understand your privilege and leverage it where you can. ••••
photographer-@b.martin ••••

text:
i've watched the qspiracy since the beginning.

steve bannon left the wh august last year and q appeared the following october. do you believe in coincidences? church militant, anyone?

abusing and leaking presidential information to mislead the people and benefit a hijacked party is obviously just business as usual.

however - while doing this djt with the brave bunch known as gop has willingly opened a pussy wound that anyone around the world can easily contaminate. i like to call it meddlin' with presidental blessin'. i'm not the only one who knows this opportunity and messes with the boombastic patriots - may be russia or china or mbs or antifa or me me me, a tiny quarter pounder sitting on me me me bed. obviously someone has a lot to lose when none of the us intelligence agencies ends this loonatic travesty.

qshow seems like a vile roleplay but instead it has become the heart of the propaganda operation that joseph goebbels would have died for. it is clear that stuff like pizzagate™ was testing and groundwork for the 2016 election and since it proved to be very effective it is used still.

the accompanying memes go way beyond the propaganda of nsdap. social media companies are helpless with the content - no way they are going to risk their business by taking responsibility.

there is absolutely no way that gop isn't aware of what is going on - after all cambridge analytica worked for ted cruz and john bolton. the whole narrative is built on the same facebook user data that bannon and the mercers reportedly got from cambridge analytica.

trump is truly playing along with his tweets, gestures and words. the bigger issue still is that republicans willingly piggybacked this lunacy while campaigning for the midterms and still keep abusing the faith of their fellow men.

this is not just an insane national security risk - it's a leaking conspiracy and treason in plain sight.

text:
yes, i know it seems like some feminists do go a little too far, but honestly, need to focus on serious topics like all forms of abuse, lgbtq inequalities, gender inequalities, racism, mental health awareness, environmentalism and everything else that is affecting us and our world.
i’ve come to realise that because the media is starting to portray feminism like this, it puts people, especially males off, because a lot think it’s about extreme women hating on them and wanting women to rule everything.
i don’t agree.
i want to empower both males, females, and non binaries.
because that’s the only way we will get equality.
